column1: Following query was issued to GS:
Technical and economic basis for the choice of a methanol production process
column2: IG Popov, NA Uvarova, NS Voronkova… - J. Appl. Chem. USSR …, 1983 - osti.gov
column12: A comparison of different processes is presented for determining the most economic method for the production of methanol. Seven variants were considered (four primary and three secondary). In all cases the low-temperature process is considered at a pressure of 29.4 …
